Cosmos University: Magic Effects Databank

This Databank contains entries on seven hundred and four magical effects, and is constantly expanding. This directory is of particular importance to our overall project goals and could be used as a starting point in researching one's own spiritual journey.

If you're interested in helping: We're currently looking to condense or expand these entries as much as possible. We are looking for suggestions on any effects that may not make sense as read, or may need to be altered to convey the correct meaning.
